{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01AqKK9UxX2a7wyGc2qzfSU1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The error is at line 68 of migrate.ts. Let me look at what's on that line. It's the `tx.unsafe(content)` call inside a transaction. The issue is that `sql.begin()` returns a TransactionSql type and the `unsafe` method is on the Sql type. Let me check the postgres.js API more carefully.\n\nActually, looking at the error message, it says `TransactionSql<{}> has no call signatures` at line 68. Let me count the lines:\n\nLine 68 is:\n```ts\n    await tx`\n      INSERT INTO _migrations (version, name) VALUES (${migration.version}, ${migration.name})\n    `;\n```\n\nWait, let me recount. The file has:\n```\nasync function applyMigration(\n  sql: postgres.Sql,\n  migration: MigrationFile,\n): Promise<void> {\n  const content = await readFile(migration.path, \"utf-8\");\n\n  await sql.begin(async (tx) => {\n    await tx.unsafe(content);\n    await tx`\n      INSERT INTO _migrations (version, name) VALUES (${migration.version}, ${migration.name})\n    `;\n  });\n}\n```\n\nLet me count from the top:\n1-14: Comments\n15: import\n\nCounting through the function definition and imports, line 68 should be the INSERT statement inside the transaction. The error about `TransactionSql<{}> has no call signatures` suggests the issue is with how I'm using the transaction object - either the `unsafe` method doesn't exist on TransactionSql, or there's a type mismatch with how the transaction is being called.\n\nLet me look at the actual postgres library types to understand what methods are available on the transaction object and how to properly execute raw SQL within a transaction. Still debugging the transaction API... The issue is specifically with `tx.unsafe()` not being available on the `TransactionSql` type—it seems the type definitions don't fully extend the `Sql` interface with all its methods. Let me try a simpler approach that doesn't rely on the `.unsafe()` method.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":334,"cache_read_input_tokens":51185,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":334},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"43f990b3-3b80-4952-b266-f65de083e062","uuid":"3a8d043d-7839-4917-9006-c78c573b04b5"}
